libusb development headers are required.

This tool came from the following thread:
http://vdrift.net/Forum/viewtopic.php?t=866

More information:
http://wiki.vdrift.net/Logitech_G25_support
http://wiki.vdrift.net/Setting_up_force_feedback

Tool options:
--verbose
--brief
--reconnect
--nativemode
--reset
--range 900

In most cases, you only need to run:
./G25manage --nativemode
and
./G25manage --range 900
